            <ul><li>unzip your application
        <li>navigate into the folder which has package.json and do 'npm install'
        <li>run 'nodemon' or 'npm run start' (Note: for this to work, you should clearly specify the starting point in package.json. I strongly recommend using express-generator to make this easy for you)
        <li>open the browser and go to "localhost:3000" (which should bring up the petition page)
        <li>add a couple of signature and see if it shows up in the table below </ul>
        <li>Please test whether your application works out of the box
        <ul><li>If necessary, you may add a clear README file</ul>
        <li>The assignment is very simple for a purpose. The evaluation scheme is all or nothing. 
        <ul><li>If you have a working application 9/10 points. On top of that, If front end looks decent, then you get the whole 10/10 points.
